snippet.title: Harry and Meghan are ‘dividing the family even more’ with rumour spreading
snippet.description:
Spiked Online’s chief political writer Brendan O’Neill says Prince Harry and wife Meghan Markle are “dividing the family even more” by spreading rumours about racist comments from family members.

“I never believed Meghan Markle’s claim in the first place,” Mr O’Neill said of Meghan Markle’s infamous claim someone in the Royal family was asking what colour her children would be.

“The idea that someone in the Royal family was making horrible, racist comments about a child that would be a child of Prince Harry – I just didn’t buy that at all.”
